data.description: ~One Level Living with over 1722 sq ft on the main level with main floor laundry. With an additional bedroom, bathroom, and family room in the unfinished basement for extra space. Nice quiet Lewiston Orchards location. New flooring, paint, appliances and more. Open floor plan in the common area lets you visit with friends and family while preparing dinner. There is plenty of lawn to play with kids and pets. "WELCOME HOME"
